					<a href="/view/thematicMap/thematicMapMain?stat_thema_map_id=EyHz6opvFy20160121115806991FE2wurICww&theme=CTGR_004&mapType=04" target="_blank" class="btnCont02">‘통계주제도>노동과 경제>농림어가수 변화’ 바로가기</a>
